					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">If you're really making a multicart, it can't really be called bank switching.<br /><br />Basically a menu loader would latch on a write to the rom area for the upper address lines beyond say A23 and then do nothing more with that latch, jumping to the start point, and having the running program not even aware of anything beyond the normal memory map.</div>

